{"tid":2186968,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"去留肝膽兩昆侖 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-09-03T10:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T10:30:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40872f962069cde9ee8f352006770590147f30b1","tid":2186968,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:30:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200903/LRHF2NQHFJGAZKRLZDLZFENNKQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200903%2FLRHF2NQHFJGAZKRLZDLZFENNKQ%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hf7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=56405815\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200903%2FLRHF2NQHFJGAZKRLZDLZFENNKQ%2F&h=dcd55628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200903/LRHF2NQHFJGAZKRLZDLZFENNKQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n去留肝膽兩昆侖 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E5aTVEEdTzsEra3lnNcrn7fq4AA=/1245x865/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OOJX6HGHPJB4DJFKEUJQL7OFHA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE5aTVEEdTzsEra3lnNcrn7fq4AA%3D%2F1245x865%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOOJX6HGHPJB4DJFKEUJQL7OFHA.png&h=bb3e1564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共政府懍於去年區議會選舉民主派大勝，遽禁今年立法會選舉，俾現屆立法會「續任至少一年」。民主派隨即掀起去留之爭：主張「留任堅守立法會戰線」者，多為傳統民主派；主張「去職抵制非法議會」者，多為新進民主派。<br />\n<br />\n主張去職者或引孔子之譽蘧伯玉：「。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n論今日民主派去留問題，其實可參考孔子另一段話：「不降其志，不辱其身，伯夷、叔齊歟（二人不事異朝）！柳下惠、少連（二人屈居下官），降志辱身矣，言中倫，行中慮，其斯而已矣（但他們言行總算得宜）。我則異於是，無可無不可（我則與他們不同，出不出仕都可以）。」而孔子雖說柳下惠降志辱身，卻顯然認為他應該做官，並批評不重用柳下惠的魯國大夫臧文仲：「臧文仲其竊位者（尸位素餐者）歟，知柳下惠之賢而不與立也。」<br />\n<br />\n然則民主派留也不留，不妨視為「無可無不可」，但去留都應「言中倫，行中慮」，更不應互相攻訐。清末譚嗣同有《獄中題壁》詩說：「我自橫刀向天笑，去留肝膽兩昆侖。」"}]}